Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Town That Welcomes Pirates?\NSetting Foot On Whisky Peak"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is with this snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was warm just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the man that fell\Nfrom the sky, Mr. Snow Barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a crude snowman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my soulful artwork,\Nthe Snow Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then! Snow Barrel Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Mr. Snow Barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Damn you!\NDamn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Hold it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come they're so energetic\Nwhen it's this cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! How much snow shoveling\Nof love would you like me to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue until\Nit stops snowing, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. Doesn't this ship have a heater?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You guys aren't guests!\NGo help shovel snow or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on\Nwith the weather around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sunny up until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next moment, it started snowing,\Nand now lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons, as well as the weather,\Ngo around randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like what Crocus-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you guys're\Nclueless about the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been steering for\Na while now. Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked the direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the ship around 180 degrees! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,180 degrees?! Why're we going back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has turned around and\Nis going in the opposite direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked away from\Nthe log pose for a second...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves were calm earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this sea, you can't trust the winds,\Nsky, waves, clouds... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that doesn't change is\Nthe direction that the log pose points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bossing me around in those\Ncozy blankets and go help already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receive the wind from the starboard!\NTurn the ship 180 degrees to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp! Take care of the lateen sail!\N--Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun! Take the helm!\N--Leave it to me, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! The wind has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first spring gale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sleep there while\Nthe snow accumulates on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I saw a dolphin jump\Nover there! Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are getting high!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see an iceberg in the\N10 o'clock direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! It's getting foggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W... We're gonna crash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Water's leaking\Nat the bottom of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to patch it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds are moving fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wind's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfurl the sails!\NThat wind is too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take it directly, we'll overturn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Eat this!\NLet's gather our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! The sail is gonna be torn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about things up here.\NGo fix the bottom of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another part of the\Nbottom of the ship damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no matter how nice the weather is,\Nyou guys shouldn't be so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better be on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you guys on this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to their town right now.\NIt's called Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we're taking them back?\NWe don't owe them anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not like it matters to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your faces say that\Nyou're thinking bad thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were your names again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Mr. 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miss Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Something has been bothering\Nme ever since I first heard your names...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard them\Nsomewhere before, or maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you sleep\Ncomfortably all this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept sleeping no matter how\Nmany times we tried to wake you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, everyone!\NWe don't know what else might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to realize\Nthe danger of this sea just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to understand the\Nreason why it's called the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it, since my\Nnavigation skills don't work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How blunt... Are we gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine! Things will\Nstill work out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Our first journey is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Whisky Peak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really a funny looking island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cacti are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for taking us home, honeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're linked by fate, we'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? We're landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a river at the front.\NLooks like we can go inland by ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't it possible that there're\Nmonsters or things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely possible.\NThis is the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we come across monsters,\Nwe can just leave the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that we have to stay\Non this island for a certain period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we store the magnetism\Nof this island in the log pose,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't go to the next island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since each island requires a different\Namount of time to store the log,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some islands require only several\Nhours while others require days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then even if this is a monster island\Nthat we want to escape from right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible that we have to stay\Nhere for days until the log is stored?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can think about that\Nwhen it happens. Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's right. Let's go.\NIt's not worth thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\NI'll protect Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait. Listen, everyone.\NMy chronic illness is suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My "do not go to the island" disease is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Listen. Make sure you're\Nprepared to run as well as fight.\N--No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well... like I said,\Nmy chronic illness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you're not listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'll appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:11:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans? Humans are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, dammit! Since it's come\Nto this, I've prepared myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters or whatever you are,\Ncome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the welcoming town, Whisky Peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F... Far from monsters,\Nwe're being welcomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates! Welcome to our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for the heroes on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There're lots of cute girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Look this way! They're handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe pirates are\Npeople's heroes after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welco...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Igarappoi.\NI'm the mayor of Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm Luffy. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, you went overboard\Non curling your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisky Peak is a town that thrives\Non making liquor and music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hospitality is the pride of our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for our proud liquor,\Nit's as bountiful as the seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you allow us\Nto throw a party for you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that we may hear your tales of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your tales of adventure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be glad to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how long will it take for the log\Nof this island to be stored?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Log? Forget such boring stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just rest after such a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone! Prepare for the party!\NSing to entertain the adventurers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I said with utter coolness,\N"Sea Kings, don't you touch my friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow...\N--Captain Usopp!\N--You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, regarding the Calm Belt,\Neven I trembled a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A tremble of excitement, that is.\N--Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Amazing!\N--Cheers to Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please don't hold back, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.\NI'd rather not drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worr...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special drink made of prime grapes\Nthat are used to make prime wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its flavor is wine itself,\Nbut it doesn't contain alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a good grape\Nharvest again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to celebrate the harvest,\Nwe'll have our usual toast competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, you continue to toast and\Nthe last one standing is the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please join in on our competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. I can't drink that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize money for the winner\Nis 100,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another cup, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! You participate, too!\NYou don't have money, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Amazing! He finished his 10th cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. I can't drink any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's downing her 12th cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! The captain finished\Na meal for 20 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cook is down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This young man is trying\Nto hit on 20 girls at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this gang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a fu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a fun night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you all\Nseem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed, I'm very glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, we failed\Nour mission of securing food...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we'd like to\Nreport that we succeeded
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in leading the gang\Nto Cactus Island. Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! If we submit this, we somehow\Nshould be able to clear our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll drop it in the\NUnluckies Box immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll deliver it for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. I quit. I'm gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! The young man is finally\Ndown after his 13th cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're hopeless, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're only two left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the 15th cup.\NShe's competing against the sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should quit soon,\Ntoo, for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! I definitely won't\Nquit until I get the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Thanks for the food.\NI can't eat any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three cooks are also down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't drink any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, what fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they wore themselves out\Npartying and fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...adventurers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again tonight the\NCactus Rocks look beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dancing under the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a poet, Igarappoi-- no, Mr. 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Since they were so stubborn,\NI added a little alcohol in their drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise they might still be\Nup and having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But was it really necessary\Nto put on an elaborate act...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for just five weak-looking brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've beat them at the harbor.\NThis town is already short of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we didn't have our hopes up\Nfor the whale meat anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to say it like that!\NWe did try our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Look at this.\NI've checked them out beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thirty million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's foolish to judge a pirate's ability\Nbased on their looks, Miss Mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-ma-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've already settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can send\Na good report to the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confiscate all the money and other\Nvaluables on the ship immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kill them, the bounty drops by 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government wants\Nto hold public executions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Capture them alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you mind letting them sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all exhausted from\Nthe journey this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 8! Miss Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy with the bellyband escaped\Nfrom the room when we weren't looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...! I thought\Nyou were completely asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsmen never make the mistake\Nof letting their guard down that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's see if I've got this right.\NThis is a nest of bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dupe pirates who are in high spirits\Nafter having just entered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there're about\N100 bounty hunters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you all... Baroque Works!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How is it that\Nyou know our company's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I used to be in a similar line of work,\NI was recruited by your company once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Employees don't know each other's\Nidentity and are called by code names.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the boss' whereabouts and his\Nidentity are also a mystery, even to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works is a criminal group that\Njust faithfully carries out their orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph...! Was it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is surprising...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know our secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we have no other\Nchoice but to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another gravestone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be added to the Cactus Rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H... He disappeared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gentle song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it there for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a wave washed away\Nthat little sand castle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up at the passing\Nclouds with a sad smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find the world is full of enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose faith
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold you in my arms forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The welcoming town is\Na nest of bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you need\Nto add only one gravestone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's eating that meat?\NI wanna eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to try out\Nthe Kitetsu III and Yubashiri
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got in Loguetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, please come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go all-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Explosion! The Three-Sword Style!\NZoro vs. Baroque Works!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
